18.title: Ray & Phillip Bahn of P.O. Bahn & Sons
18.plot: P.O. Bahn and Sons opened for business selling automotive parts in Santa Monica in 1927. Today, P.O. Bahn's grandson Ray and great grandson Phillip still offer their loyal customers a large array of saws and tools at their store.

19.title: Make Music LA in Santa Monica

20.title: Gilbert's El Indio in Santa Monica
20.plot: Gilbert's El Indio at 2526 Pico Blvd in Santa Monica, was opened on May 20, 1974, and is still run by the same family. They still serve delicious authentic Mexican family-style meals.
